snippet.textDisplay: I once had a really good walking stick. It was the best stick anyone has ever found. I would constantly test its limits. It had this strange property of absorbing any kinetic energy. At one point my little brother got mad for beating him in a game we were playing. He jammed the stick into a hole underneath the driveway. He bent it to the point that the tip broke off and ruined the stick.  RIP Stick 2014-2019. Anyway, when it was still alive, I am 99.99% percent sure that I once said it's better than bacon.
